        "title_e": "原子力発電所で事故があった福島県大熊町に役場が戻る",
        "date": "2019-05-07",
        "urlnormal": "https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20190507/k10011907461000.html",
        "urleasy": "https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/easy/k10011907461000/k10011907461000.html"
